zzapper wrote:
> One of my scripts (don't know which) is laying a file named 0 size 0 in various directories.
> Any "polite" clues as to what might be producing them?

That's not the easiest thing to search for.

Try removing write permissions from the 0 files and then wait for one of
your scripts to fail.

